    <h1>Social Media Algorithm</h1>
    <p class="description">The set of rules and machine learning models that determines which content each user sees in their feed — and in what order — based on <strong>predicted engagement, relevance signals, and platform objectives</strong>.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
